headline.print_headline: Inefficiency Hurts U.S. In Ranking Of Health
headline.seo: Health Care Inefficiency Is Blamed for Low Longevity Ranking of U.S.
headline.main: Inefficiency Hurts U.S. in Longevity Rankings

docs.lead_paragraph: Researchers have concluded that the inefficiency of the health care system is to blame for the United States’ ranking of 49th in life expectancy.
